      • uploadFile

        public void uploadFile(javax.faces.event.ActionEvent ae)
        Method for uploading a file. File to be uploaded is represented as part. Then, InputStream is retrieved from that part and translated into array of bytes. After that appropriate fields of file are set to accomplish file uploading to database.
        Parameters:
        ae - ActionEvent - represents the activation of a user interface component (such as a UIComponent).
